data.description:
Come see this well-maintained 3 Bed 2 Bath home located in Castle Rock Addition in Mustang Schools!  Convenientlly located with easy access to the Kilpatrick Turnpike and close to restaurants and shopping. Great floorplan with a spacious living room and cozy fireplace that opens to the dining and kitchen areas which makes a perfect home for entertaining friends and family!  The primary bedroom with en suite provides a private sanctuary for the owners with great closet and storage space.  The secondary bedrooms are a good size with easy access to the additional bathroom.  Step out back to the spacious patio area with a hot tub and ready for pool time and summer cookouts.  

Buyer to verify all information including school district, taxes and square footage. 
Call and schedule a showing today!
